query.content: SELECT t FROM TvlRqt t WHERE t.uerId = :uerId AND t.Sas = :Sas ORDER BY t.persistenceId ASC

query.name: findByOrgUnitNumAndhksxvzeeID

query.name: queryByVariousFields
query.content: SELECT c FROM hbwsxcdfgdfghts c WHERE ( (:caseId IS NOT NULL and c.caseId = :caseId) OR (:caseId IS NULL) ) AND ( (:pesIds IS NOT NULL and :pesIds like CONCAT('%', c.pesDefinitionId, '%')) OR (:pesIds IS NULL) ) AND ( (:partyType IS NOT NULL and c.partyType = :partyType) OR (:partyType IS NULL) ) AND ( (:partyufrms IS NOT NULL and c.partyufrms = :partyufrms) OR (:partyufrms IS NULL) ) AND ( (:Sas IS NOT NULL and c.Sas = :Sas) OR (:Sas IS NULL) ) AND ( (:caseOwnerufrms IS NOT NULL and c.caseOwnerufrms = :caseOwnerufrms) OR (:caseOwnerufrms IS NULL) ) AND ( (:ldnsmcxlingUnitCode IS NOT NULL and c.ldnsmcxlingUnitCode = :ldnsmcxlingUnitCode) OR (:ldnsmcxlingUnitCode IS NULL) ) ORDER BY c.caseId ASC

query.name: countFqrQueryByVariousFields
query.content: SELECT count(c) FROM hbwsxcdfgdfghts c WHERE ( (:caseId IS NOT NULL and c.caseId = :caseId) OR (:caseId IS NULL) ) AND ( (:pesIds IS NOT NULL and :pesIds like CONCAT('%', c.pesDefinitionId, '%')) OR (:pesIds IS NULL) ) AND ( (:partyType IS NOT NULL and c.partyType = :partyType) OR (:partyType IS NULL) ) AND ( (:partyufrms IS NOT NULL and c.partyufrms = :partyufrms) OR (:partyufrms IS NULL) ) AND ( (:Sas IS NOT NULL and c.Sas = :Sas) OR (:Sas IS NULL) ) AND ( (:caseOwnerufrms IS NOT NULL and c.caseOwnerufrms = :caseOwnerufrms) OR (:caseOwnerufrms IS NULL) ) AND ( (:ldnsmcxlingUnitCode IS NOT NULL and c.ldnsmcxlingUnitCode = :ldnsmcxlingUnitCode) OR (:ldnsmcxlingUnitCode IS NULL) )

query.name: findWWAPReqFqrAdting
query.content:
SELECT Rqtpoklwxs
FROM SAFAklwnytalWithoutAcadPenjnszl Rqtpoklwxs
JOIN FETCH Rqtpoklwxs.hbwsxcdfgdfghts hbwsxcdfgdfghts JOIN FETCH Rqtpoklwxs.RqtHistory Rqteet JOIN FETCH Rqteet.uploadedduns uploadeddun
WHERE ( (:caseId IS NOT NULL and hbwsxcdfgdfghts.caseId = :caseId) OR (:caseId IS NULL) ) AND ( (:Sas IS NOT NULL AND ( (:Sas = 'Active' AND (:activeSases LIKE (concat('%',hbwsxcdfgdfghts.Sas,'%')))) OR (:Sas = 'Completed' AND (:completedSases LIKE (concat('%',hbwsxcdfgdfghts.Sas,'%')))) ) ) OR (:Sas IS NULL) ) AND ( (:pesIds IS NOT NULL and (:pesIds LIKE (concat('%',hbwsxcdfgdfghts.pesDefinitionId,'%')))) OR (:pesIds IS NULL) ) AND ( (:dunType IS NOT NULL and uploadeddun.dunType = :dunType) OR (:dunType IS NULL) ) AND ( (:AdtSas IS NOT NULL AND ( (:AdtSas = :blankAdtSas AND uploadeddun.verificationSas = null) OR uploadeddun.verificationSas = :AdtSas) ) OR (:AdtSas IS NULL) )
ORDER BY Rqtpoklwxs.persistenceId ASC
